# 91.不同路径  
```java
// DP,同最小路径和,人为定义“假起点”
class Solution {
    public int uniquePaths(int m, int n) {
        int[][] f = new int[m + 1][n + 1];
        f[0][1] = 1;//“假起点”
        for (int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
                f[i + 1][j + 1] = f[i][j + 1] + f[i + 1][j];
            }
        }
        return f[m][n];
    }
}
```
