## 92.最小路径和
```java  
class Solution {
    public int minPathSum(int[][] grid) {
        int m = grid.length;
        int n = grid[0].length;
        int[][] f = new int[m+1][n+1];
        for(int j=0;j<n+1;j++){
            f[0][j] = Integer.MAX_VALUE; 
        }
        f[0][1] = 0;
        for(int i=0;i<m;i++){
            f[i+1][0] = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
            for(int j=0;j<n;j++){
                f[i+1][j+1] = Math.min(f[i+1][j],f[i][j+1])+grid[i][j];
            }
        }
        return f[m][n];
    }
}
```
